 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/malcolmmacgregor/4085327737/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2587/4085327737_f1e41177d6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\"></a></p>\n<p>Good morning, Nashville. We&#x2019;re pretty sure that we&#x2019;re loving Chris Johnson more and more by the day. After <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/200911041540/SPORTS01/91104068\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">bribing his entire offensive line with new cars</a> and <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/sports/entertainer-johnson-dines-faith-hill\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">sharing a heart-to-heart with Faith Hill over Swett&#x2019;s</a> on Tuesday, <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20091112/SPORTS01/911120350/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">he&#x2019;s  now saying that he has a special party planned if the Titans keep winning</a>. In case you&#x2019;ve forgotten what happened the last time he promised us that, <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=88hQPXEnJDM&amp;feature=related\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.youtube.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">it&#x201D;s all on Youtube</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20091112/NEWS01/911120354/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">28% increase in Tennessee&#x2019;s known cases of HIV/AIDS have caused a shortage of financial resources that help pay for treatment for those who can&#x2019;t afford it</a>. Half of those living with the disease in Tennessee are in the middle Tennessee region.</li>\n<li>Our state seems to be falling apart these days. <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/3bd3967c-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">A third big rockslide happened near Chattanooga last night around 11pm</a> following that other rockslide on I-40 over the North Carolina boarder and the one that was <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/11/11/rockslide-in-tennessee-ca_n_354003.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.huffingtonpost.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">caught on video</a> in Polk County. Several parts of the state have also been rocked by earthquakes in the past week or two.</li>\n<li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces. </strong>Congratulations to Taylor Swift for <a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=12578\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">cleaning up at the CMAs last night</a> &#x2026; Metro would like everyone&#x2019;s advice on <a href=\"http://politics.nashvillepost.com/2009/11/11/metro-looks-for-input/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;politics.nashvillepost.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">how to use the internet</a> &#x2026; Kingston residents continue to say that the <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20091112/NEWS01/911120336/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">TVA isn&#x2019;t being fair about compensation</a> for the ash spill &#x2026; The <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=11489982\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">fate of Councilwoman Pam Murray</a> is decided today in a special recall election for District 5.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/malcolmmacgregor/4085327737/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">MalcolmMacGregor</a>.</em></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/13/bright-early-sign-of-the-times-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Sign Of The Times Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Sign Of The Times Edition</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/07/04/happy-hour-celebrate-good-times-we-lose/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: Celebrate Good Times (We Lose)\">Happy Hour: Celebrate Good Times (We Lose)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/03/25/bright-early-tough-times-ahead-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Tough Times Ahead Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Tough Times Ahead Edition</a></li>\n</ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"
